title: Diet Hobbit Part 1.mp4
description:
DIET HOBBIT: PART 1

A fan edit of the first half of Peter Jackson's Hobbit trilogy, cutting out OVER 50% of the material to create a fast-paced adventure film centered around Bilbo Baggins.

The film includes the events of An Unexpected Journey, and the first half of The Desolation Of Smaug.

No White Council, no Radagast, less Azog, less Elves, less Thorin-centric storytelling. Enjoy!



Runtime: 2hrs 9min
